License: GPL 3
Description: RevERS
        ======
        
        .. contents:
        
        Extract DB structure into `Storm <http://storm.canonical.com>`_ classes set.
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        ::
        
            $ mkdir models
            $ revers.py postgres://user:password@host/database
            $ ls models
            __db__.py  __init__.py  public.py  <schemes>.py
        
